propertiesFile.name: macros
propertiesFile.content:
---
version: 2
macros:
- name: "cents"
  description: "This is cents macro"
  arguments:
  - name: "column_name"
    type: "unknown"
  - name: "decimal_places"
    type: "int"
    description: "Field with default value"
  macroType: "expression"
- name: "audit"
  arguments:
  - name: "table_name"
    type: "unknown"
    description: "Name of the table"
  macroType: "query"
- name: "nestedMacroName"
  description: "This is nested"
  arguments:
  - name: "column_name"
    type: "unknown"
  macroType: "expression"
